在原项目上添加了隐藏候选栏配置。提供了一个脚本（hide_kimpanel.sh）来切换此选项。可通过系统快捷键绑定到脚本来快速切换。


Added hidden candidate column configuration on the original project. 
A script (hide_kimpanel. sh) is provided to switch this option.
It can be quickly switched by binding to the script through system shortcut keys.

KDE's kimpanel implementation for GNOME Shell

Install requirements
gettext
cmake

If you'd like to install it as user, run ./install.sh under the root of source.

Translation: https://www.transifex.com/fcitx/fcitx/gnome-shell-extensions-kimpanel/
